data.description: Welcome to this adorable turn-key property. Whether you're looking to live within walking distance to BSU or hoping to use as a rental - this beautiful home is ready for you! Boasting new windows, window coverings, a new smart thermostat, a new reverse osmosis water system and a fully remodeled bathroom. AC & gas water heater are newer. The fully fenced back yard has mature landscaping with a covered patio to enjoy a quiet evening around the firepit. NO HOA. RV parking. Property has great development potential to add another unit on 2 deeded lots.
